# OpenSCAD

Use [OpenSCAD documentation](https://openscad.org/documentation.html) as the reference for:

- **Language Reference**: Primitives, transformations, boolean ops, modules, functions
- **Tutorial**: Parameterization, control flow, loops, extrusion
- **User Manual**: Import/export, paths, libraries, customizer

Project layout:
- `src/openscad/projects/` — per-project .scad files
- `src/openscad/lib/` — shared modules and libraries (BOSL2, etc.)
